headline: Realty Income's Strategic Partnerships: Will it Boost Growth?

headline: Simon Property Group: Cash-Leasing-Spread Compounding at Scale
summary: At a low-teens FFO multiple and mid-single-digit yield, sustained spreads support 6--8% FFO growth and a 9--12% total return without re-rating.
